Invite observers in the procurement activities consistent with the requirements of Section 13 of the 2016 Revised IRR of RA No. 9184;
Verify the completeness of the offer of bidder in the conduct of detailed evaluation to ensure that offer address or provide all the required items in the bidding documents; and
